We have moved 9 times since our wedding 50 years ago, and have always found that natives depended on us to tell them things about where they have lived their whole lives. Example: my husband moved to Milwaukee while I still lived in NJ, in a bad real estate market, waiting for our house to sell. He had no car, and went everywhere by bus or foot. 

